Package: littletrees
Type: Package
Title: Little's Atlas of United States Trees
Version: 0.1.0
Author: William K. Petry [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5230-5987>>)
Maintainer: William K. Petry <william.petry@usys.ethz.ch>
Description: Provides range maps for 679 tree (sub)species from the United
    States of America as simple features, cloned from the United States
    Geological Survey's "Digital Representations of Tree Species Range Maps
    from 'Atlas of United States Trees' by Elbert L. Little, Jr. (and other
    publications)."
URL: https://github.com/wpetry/littletrees
BugReports: https://github.com/wpetry/littletrees/issues
License: Creative Commons Zero (CC0, public domain)
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: sf (>= 0.6-3)
Suggests: rgdal, rgeos, spatstat, dplyr (>= 0.7-0), tidyr (>= 0.7-2),
    tibble (>= 1.4.1), ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1.900)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
